org.apache.flink.api.java.functions

Annotation Type FunctionAnnotation.ReadFieldsFirst


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public static @interface FunctionAnnotation.ReadFieldsFirst
    Specifies the fields of the second input value of a user-defined that are accessed in the code. This annotation can only be used with user-defined functions with two inputs (Join, Cross, ...).
